function Dyes {
	.@master = getarg(0);
	.@dyed = getarg(1);
	.@zeny = getarg(2);
	if (.masterscount)
		for (.@i = 1; .@i <= .masterscount;.@i++) {
			if (.@master == getd(".masters"+.@i)) {
				.@exist = .@i;
				break;
			}
		}
	if (!.@exist) {
		.masterscount++;
		.@mcount = .masterscount;
		setd ".masters"+.@mcount,.@master;
	} else {
		.@mcount = .@exist;
	}
	
	
	for (.@i = 1; .@i < getd(".dcount"+.@mcount);.@i++) {
		if (.@dyed == getd(".dyed"+.@i)) {
			return;
		}
	}
	
	setd ".dcount"+.@mcount,getd(".dcount"+.@mcount)+1;
	.@dcount = getd(".dcount"+.@mcount);
	setd ".dyed"+.@mcount+"_"+.@dcount, .@dyed;
	setd ".zeny"+.@mcount+"_"+.@dcount, .@zeny;
	
	for (.@i = 3; .@i < getargcount();.@i+=2) {
			setarray getd(".req"+.@mcount+"_"+.@dcount+"["+(.@i-3)+"]"), getarg(.@i);
			setarray getd(".amt"+.@mcount+"_"+.@dcount+"["+(.@i+1-3)+"]"), getarg(.@i+1);
	}
	return;
}
